<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2013/05/04/morphing-tiles/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Morphing Tiles">Morphing Tiles</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p><a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/tiles_hex_progressive3shortBW.gif"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3038" title="tiles_hex_progressive3shortBW" src="http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/tiles_hex_progressive3shortBW.gif" alt="morphing islamic tiles" width="500" height="281" /></a></p>
<p>My animated tile experiments continue. Even though I&#8217;m designing in color, I had to make this animated gif small and black-and-white to fit within WordPress&#8217;s 2MB upload limit.</p>
<p>I am very pleased with how this is going.</p>
<div class="plus-one-wrap"><g:plusone href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2013/05/04/morphing-tiles/"></g:plusone></div><div class="addtoany_share_save_container"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="wpa2a_13"><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save" style="background:url(http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/favicon.png) no-repeat scroll 4px 0px !important;padding:0 0 0 25px;display:inline-block;height:16px;vertical-align:middle">Share/Bookmark</a></div></div><p class="wp-flattr-button"><a class="FlattrButton" style="display:none;" href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2013/05/04/morphing-tiles/" title=" Morphing Tiles" rev="flattr;uid:ninapaley;language:en_GB;category:text;tags:blog;button:compact;">My animated tile experiments continue. Even though I&#8217;m designing in color, I had to make this animated gif small and black-and-white to fit within WordPress&#8217;s 2MB upload limit. I am...</a></p></div>

<div class="post-footer">May 4th, 2013 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/animation/" title="View all posts in Animation" rel="category tag">Animation</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/design/" title="View all posts in design" rel="category tag">design</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/tiles/" title="View all posts in tiles" rel="category tag">tiles</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/work-in-progress/" title="View all posts in work-in-progress" rel="category tag">work-in-progress</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2013/05/04/morphing-tiles/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on Morphing Tiles">4 comments</a> </div>
